    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>很多情况下会遇到推导公式的时候需要连等的情况，aligned 基本上能满足大部分需要。这里先把代码简单放上来。</p>
<figure class="highlight tex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="formula">$$<span class="command">\begin</span><span class="special">&#123;</span>aligned<span class="special">&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line">    V(s) <span class="special">&amp;</span>amp; =  <span class="command">\frac</span><span class="special">&#123;</span>A<span class="special">&#125;</span><span class="special">&#123;</span>s<span class="special">&#125;</span>+<span class="command">\frac</span><span class="special">&#123;</span>Bs+C<span class="special">&#125;</span><span class="special">&#123;</span>s^2+6s+25<span class="special">&#125;</span><span class="command">\\</span></span><br><span class="line">    -<span class="command">\frac</span><span class="special">&#123;</span>24s^2+144s-2500<span class="special">&#125;</span><span class="special">&#123;</span>s(s^2+6s+25)<span class="special">&#125;</span> <span class="special">&amp;</span>amp; =  <span class="command">\frac</span><span class="special">&#123;</span>A<span class="special">&#125;</span><span class="special">&#123;</span>s<span class="special">&#125;</span>+<span class="command">\frac</span><span class="special">&#123;</span>Bs+C<span class="special">&#125;</span><span class="special">&#123;</span>s^2+6s+25<span class="special">&#125;</span><span class="command">\\</span></span><br><span class="line">    -24s^2-144s+2500 <span class="special">&amp;</span>amp; = A(s^2+6s+25)+(Bs+C)s<span class="command">\\</span></span><br><span class="line">    -24s^2-144s+2500 <span class="special">&amp;</span>amp; = (A+B)s^2+(6A+C)s+25A<span class="command">\\</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="command">\end</span><span class="special">&#123;</span>aligned<span class="special">&#125;</span>$$</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>注意到这里最重要的一点是整个包必须是在数学模式下的，其次就是’&amp;’定义了整个公式的对齐方式，一般情况下放在等号的左边，具体情况类似表格。</p>
]]></content>
