    <title><![CDATA[[LaTeX] 关于段落缩进]]></title>
    <link href="http://stevewang1007.github.io/2015/10/19/%5BLaTeX%5D%20%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E%E6%AE%B5%E8%90%BD%E7%BC%A9%E8%BF%9B/"/>
    <id>http://stevewang1007.github.io/2015/10/19/[LaTeX] 关于段落缩进/</id>
    <published>2015-10-20T02:49:06.000Z</published>
    <updated>2016-03-15T18:59:11.000Z</updated>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>接着上一篇文章继续说，在写assignment的过程中， 假设你已经在左侧插了图片，开始在右侧写答案，这时如果文字超过了图片，文字就会自动回复正常的缩进，但是你是一个一用$\LaTeX$就会变成处女座的人，总是希望自己的证明过程在右边整齐的排成一列，怎么做呢？</p>
<p>当然你可以使用神奇的<code>\qquad</code> 比如这样：</p>
<figure class="highlight tex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="formula">$$<span class="command">\qquad</span> <span class="command">\qquad</span> <span class="command">\qquad</span> <span class="command">\qquad</span> <span class="command">\ </span><span class="command">\alpha</span> I_0=-I'$$</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="formula">$$<span class="command">\qquad</span> <span class="command">\qquad</span> <span class="command">\qquad</span> <span class="command">\qquad</span> <span class="command">\ </span> <span class="command">\,</span> V_0=I'<span class="command">\frac</span><span class="special">&#123;</span>R_3R_4<span class="special">&#125;</span><span class="special">&#123;</span>R_3+R_4<span class="special">&#125;</span>$$</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="formula">$$<span class="command">\qquad</span> <span class="command">\qquad</span> <span class="command">\qquad</span> <span class="command">\qquad</span> <span class="command">\ </span> <span class="command">\,</span> V_s=I_0(R_1+R_2)$$</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="formula">$$<span class="command">\qquad</span> <span class="command">\qquad</span> <span class="command">\qquad</span> <span class="command">\qquad</span> <span class="command">\ </span> <span class="command">\,</span> <span class="command">\left</span> |<span class="command">\frac</span><span class="special">&#123;</span>V_0<span class="special">&#125;</span><span class="special">&#123;</span>V_s<span class="special">&#125;</span><span class="command">\right</span>|=<span class="command">\left</span> |<span class="command">\frac</span><span class="special">&#123;</span>R_3R_4I'<span class="special">&#125;</span><span class="special">&#123;</span>I_0(R_1+R_2)(R_3+R_4)<span class="special">&#125;</span><span class="command">\right</span>|=10$$</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>有点丧心病狂是不是？ 我也是这么觉得的…… 但是只要整齐美观什么都可以放弃的，对吧？<br>当然还有更简单的方法，</p>
<figure class="highlight tex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="command">\documentclass</span><span class="special">[</span>letterpaper,10pt<span class="special">]</span><span class="special">&#123;</span>article<span class="special">&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="command">\begin</span><span class="special">&#123;</span>document<span class="special">&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="command">\hfill</span><span class="command">\begin</span><span class="special">&#123;</span>minipage<span class="special">&#125;</span><span class="special">&#123;</span>0.7<span class="command">\textwidth</span><span class="special">&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="formula">$$-v_s+R_2(i_1-i_3)+R_4(i_1-i_2)=0$$</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="formula">$$-1<span class="command">\,</span>V+1<span class="command">\,</span><span class="command">\Omega</span> (i_1-i_3)+1<span class="command">\,</span><span class="command">\Omega</span>(i_1-i_2)=0$$</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="formula">$$2i_1-i_2-i_3-1<span class="command">\,</span>V=0$$</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="command">\begin</span><span class="special">&#123;</span>equation<span class="special">&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line">        2i_1-1=i_2+i_3</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="command">\end</span><span class="special">&#123;</span>equation<span class="special">&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="formula">$<span class="command">\qquad</span> <span class="command">\qquad</span>$</span> 3<span class="command">\.</span> Apply KVL to mesh 2, <span class="formula">$$-v_4+v_3+v_5=0$$</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="formula">$$R_4(i_2-i_1)+R_3(i_2-i_3)+R_5i_2=0$$</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="command">\begin</span><span class="special">&#123;</span>equation<span class="special">&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line">        3i_2=i_1+i_3</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="command">\end</span><span class="special">&#123;</span>equation<span class="special">&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="formula">$<span class="command">\qquad</span> <span class="command">\qquad</span>$</span> 4<span class="command">\.</span> Apply KVL to mesh 3, <span class="formula">$$v_1-v_3-v_2=0$$</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="formula">$$R_1i_3+R_3(i_3-i_2)+R_2(i_3-i_1)=0$$</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="formula">$$i_3+i_3-i_2+i_3-i_1=0$$</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="command">\end</span><span class="special">&#123;</span>minipage<span class="special">&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="command">\end</span><span class="special">&#123;</span>document<span class="special">&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>虽然还是有很多数学空格但是至少没那么丧心病狂了。 注意事项：1. 注意有\hfill不然不会起作用。\hfill 填充了左侧的空白所以才能缩进，一定不能忘。 2. minipage 的参数设定的是block内文字的宽度。 3. 如果block内的文字超出了页面范围整个block都会换到下一页去，至于latex如何判断是否超出页面至今没有搞懂，多尝试几次或者你已经掌握了规律请在下面留言。4. 可以和wrapfigure 搭配使用，但是图片会和整个block平行，所以自己选择。 5. 内容什么的就不要管了，反正我也看不懂。</p>
]]></content>
